{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/jekyll/visible-datetime/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"JIKOID","description":"천천히 그리고 꾸준히"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"94c3e4da-41d8-5a17-be30-9b34b1b32599","excerpt":"이번에는 Github 블로그에 시간을 표시해보려고 한다.\n 현재 상태 확인하기 기본 minimal mistakes…","html":"<p>이번에는 Github 블로그에 시간을 표시해보려고 한다.\n<br></p>\n<h2 id=\"현재-상태-확인하기\">현재 상태 확인하기</h2>\n<p>기본 minimal mistakes 테마에서는 읽는 시간만 표시되고 날짜는 표시되지 않는다.</p>\n<div style=\"padding: 0 200px;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/061fa8cc526a669b10c753dfdbcca6ed/e4900/image.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 18.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/061fa8cc526a669b10c753dfdbcca6ed/0a47e/image.png\" srcset=\"/static/061fa8cc526a669b10c753dfdbcca6ed/8a4e8/image.png 150w,\n/static/061fa8cc526a669b10c753dfdbcca6ed/5a46d/image.png 300w,\n/static/061fa8cc526a669b10c753dfdbcca6ed/0a47e/image.png 600w,\n/static/061fa8cc526a669b10c753dfdbcca6ed/1cfc2/image.png 900w,\n/static/061fa8cc526a669b10c753dfdbcca6ed/e4900/image.png 988w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n<br>\n<p>그래서 시간이 표시되도록 수정해보려고 한다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"읽는-시간을-표시해주는-소스-찾기\">읽는 시간을 표시해주는 소스 찾기</h2>\n<p>먼저 읽는 시간을 표시하고 있는 페이지의 html 소스 파일을 찾아보면 <code class=\"language-text\">_includes/archive-single.html</code> 에서 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{% raw %}{% include page__meta.html type=include.type %}{% endraw %}</code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<p>바로 위의 코드와 같이 <code class=\"language-text\">page__meta.html</code> 파일을 include 해서 읽는 시간을 보여주고 있는 것을 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>그럼 <code class=\"language-text\">page__meta.html</code> 파일로 가서 시간을 표시하는 부분을 찾아보았다.</p>\n<p>해당 페이지를 살펴보니 이 부분을 통해 시간을 보여줄 수 있을 것이라고 생각이 되었다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">{% raw %}{% if document.show_date and document.date %}\n  {% assign date = document.date %}\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>page__meta-date<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>i</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>far {% if include.type == 'grid' and document.read_time and document.show_date %}fa-fw {% endif %}fa-calendar-alt<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-hidden</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>true<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>i</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    {% assign date_format = site.date_format | default: \"%B %-d, %Y\" %}\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>time</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">datetime</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>{{ date | date_to_xmlschema }}<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>{{ date | date: date_format }}<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>time</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n{% endif %}{% endraw %}</code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"시간을-보여주는-옵션-적용하기\">시간을 보여주는 옵션 적용하기</h2>\n<p>document, 즉 포스트 안에 show_date 옵션이 true 이면 날짜를 보여주는 조건을 확인할 수 있었고 현재 사이트의 날짜 기준으로 <code class=\"language-text\">%B %-d, %Y</code> 으로 보여주고 있어서 바로 <code class=\"language-text\">show_date</code> 옵션을 적용해보았다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">---</span>\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Github 블로그 시간 표시하기 (Minimal Mistakes)\"</span>\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">tags</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> github minimal_mistakes datetime\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">categories</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> github_jekyll\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">layout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> single\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">author_profile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">true</span>\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">toc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">true</span>\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">toc_sticky</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">true</span>\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">show_date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">true</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">---</span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<p>그랬더니 다음과 같이 시간이 표시되었다.</p>\n<div style=\"padding: 0 200px;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/6afd5fe98ba3f1bf837c0310ee07a6e9/f1901/image2.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 21.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image2\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/6afd5fe98ba3f1bf837c0310ee07a6e9/0a47e/image2.png\" srcset=\"/static/6afd5fe98ba3f1bf837c0310ee07a6e9/8a4e8/image2.png 150w,\n/static/6afd5fe98ba3f1bf837c0310ee07a6e9/5a46d/image2.png 300w,\n/static/6afd5fe98ba3f1bf837c0310ee07a6e9/0a47e/image2.png 600w,\n/static/6afd5fe98ba3f1bf837c0310ee07a6e9/1cfc2/image2.png 900w,\n/static/6afd5fe98ba3f1bf837c0310ee07a6e9/f1901/image2.png 942w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n<br>\n<p>하지만 나는 <code class=\"language-text\">2024-06-12</code> 의 날짜 형태로 보여주고 싶었기 때문에 해당 부분의 날짜 포맷을 변경해주었다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>변경 전 ( <code class=\"language-text\">%B %-d, %Y</code> )</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{% raw %}{% assign date_format = site.date_format | default: \"%B %-d, %Y\" %}{% endraw %}</code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li>변경 후 ( <code class=\"language-text\">%Y-%m-%d</code> )</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{% raw %}{% assign date_format = site.date_format | default: \"%Y-%m-%d\" %}{% endraw %}</code></pre></div>\n<p>그리고 다시 확인해보니 잘 적용된 것을 확인할 수 있었다.</p>\n<div style=\"padding: 0 200px;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/e3a4a962df916529c2b23bc11f40e599/906b5/image3.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 20.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image3\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/e3a4a962df916529c2b23bc11f40e599/0a47e/image3.png\" srcset=\"/static/e3a4a962df916529c2b23bc11f40e599/8a4e8/image3.png 150w,\n/static/e3a4a962df916529c2b23bc11f40e599/5a46d/image3.png 300w,\n/static/e3a4a962df916529c2b23bc11f40e599/0a47e/image3.png 600w,\n/static/e3a4a962df916529c2b23bc11f40e599/1cfc2/image3.png 900w,\n/static/e3a4a962df916529c2b23bc11f40e599/906b5/image3.png 950w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</div>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<p>날짜 보여주기 완료!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Github 블로그 시간 표시하기 (Minimal Mistakes)","date":"2024년 06월 12일","description":"Github Jekyll 블로그에서 시간의 포맷을 변경하여 적용한 내용입니다.","tags":["github","minimal_mistakes","datetime"],"categories":"blog/jekyll"},"tab